---
import { PhoneCall, FileText, CheckCircle2 } from 'lucide-astro'
---

<section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900">Así te ayudo a contratar</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-600">Proceso simple, pensado para familias y adultos mayores.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-blue-700 font-black text-lg">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100">1</span>
          <span>Conversemos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-start gap-3">
          <PhoneCall class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-700" />
          <p class="text-slate-600">Me llamas o escribes por WhatsApp y te atiendo directamente.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-blue-700 font-black text-lg">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100">2</span>
          <span>Revisamos tu caso</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-start gap-3">
          <FileText class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-700" />
          <p class="text-slate-600">Te hago preguntas simples y te explico opciones claras.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white border border-slate-100 p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-blue-700 font-black text-lg">
          <span class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-100">3</span>
          <span>Contratamos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex items-start gap-3">
          <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-700" />
          <p class="text-slate-600">Te envío la propuesta y activamos tu plan en el mismo día.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
